//Using infinite while loop, write and execute a program to that expects user to give only a specific type of input otherwise raise error. Handle eroor using try- except.


while True:
x_str = input('Please enter an even number:')
try:
x = int(x_str)
if x%2==0:
print("Thank you!")
break
else:
print("input is odd number")
continue
except:
print("Invalid input!!")
              
